{"tid":1694720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息人士否認周同學即將拔喉","createTime":"2019-11-05T09:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T09:38:10.000Z","uid":336865,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b27e5a78d0ad9b9de621b7bebd07bd0dd75814","tid":1694720,"uid":336865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"消息：墮樓科大生疑現腦幹死亡迹象 (16:14)<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日（4日）凌晨於將軍澳發射催淚彈驅散示威者，科技大學22歲男生其後被發現倒臥尚德邨停車場重創，兩次腦部手術仍未能控制腦水腫及出血情況。據本報兩個可靠消息渠道獲悉，科大生疑出現腦幹死亡迹象，包括瞳孔放大。其中一個消息人士表示，傷者「兩邊（瞳孔）一開始已經無乜反應」。醫管局表示，截至下午3點，科大生仍情況危殆，留醫深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n傷者的家屬下午3時許抵達醫院，另有一男一女市民到醫院為傷者祈禱。消息人士否認傷者即將拔喉。<br />\n<br />\n根據非牟利慈善團體香港腦科基金網頁資料，要證實傷者腦幹死亡需要兩名醫生各自進行測試，包括雙眼瞳孔是否對光線全無反應、雙側角膜反射均消失、耳朵被灌凍水後，雙眼有否左右移動等，最後才會進行窒息測試，即拔喉後病人不能自主呼吸，合共7個測試。此外，判定腦死亡，需要觀察一段時間，長短視乎導致昏迷的原因而定，但不能少於4小時。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191105/s00001/1572940878754/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE%E8%85%A6%E5%B9%B9%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E8%BF%B9%E8%B1%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00001%2F1572940878754%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%2585%25A6%25E5%25B9%25B9%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E8%25BF%25B9%25E8%25B1%25A1&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=b30ad098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00001%2F1572940878754%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%2585%25A6%25E5%25B9%25B9%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E8%25BF%25B9%25E8%25B1%25A1&h=b71fae77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191105/s00001/1572940878754/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE%E8%85%A6%E5%B9%B9%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E8%BF%B9%E8%B1%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家集氣! 科大手足撐住啊!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66cd2a5a14891b5eca8969035499d5b6899593d","tid":1694720,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &lt;&lt;&lt; 依個唔係喊既 emoji <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請用依幾個"},{"pid":"57e0ab42e05a878bb5be5ec556e0b2b3fc794b28","tid":1694720,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"撐住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b8173a62cdb8d5fc0144eaf72ed0bcbc38a9c2","tid":1694720,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39e83af521132f94f979860f0c6fdfe8bf0a093","tid":1694720,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"要吉人天相"}]}